title: Nova Fractal - Through Our Senses (Sky Technology Remix)
description:
► Subscribe: http://bit.ly/SubscribeNeogoa

Sky Technology & Nova Fractal return with a brand new collaborative release, Versus, featuring reciprocal remixes and a joint production showcasing their melodic new school Goa trance style. Download Versus - http://www.neogoa.net/versus

01 - Nova Fractal - Through Our Senses (Sky Technology Remix) (145 BPM) 
02 - Sky Technology vs Nova Fractal - Dark Energy (Versus Mix) (146 BPM) 
03 - Sky Technology - Back To The Future (Nova Fractal Remix) (145 BPM)
